  "signal_description": "The query retrieves the month, percentage of automated events, and company name from the 'defaultview-225' table. It first selects the earliest end time of events with the name 'Post Invoice' and truncates it to the month level. Then, it calculates the percentage of events created by system or service users compared to all events. This percentage is multiplied by 100. Finally, it selects the 'Inv. Company Code Text' column and filters out rows where it is null. The results are ordered by the month in ascending order and filled with null values for missing months."
